## üß± Typesetting Rules

### Padding & Bounding Boxes
- Line height determines bounding box size
- Vertically center-align text within containers
- Maintain even padding above and below text

### Baseline Usage
- Anchor text position using the **baseline**, not bounding box
- Android/Material UIs rely on baseline distance for spacing
- Avoid measuring by "top" or "center" when baseline spec exists

